column3: ...Hm? I can't very well dispose of something you don't have, now, can I?

...Really? Well, I suppose the moldy old book \x02\x1a\x02\x02\x03was\x02\x1a\x02\x01\x03 bound for the furnace any\xe2\x94\x80errr...I mean, it breaks my heart to see a piece of history treated like so many pages of soiled parchment, but who am I to argue with a customer?
All progress within \x021\x11\xff\nEventItem\x03\xe8\x02\x02\x02\x03 will be lost. Are you certain you wish to proceed?
There. It's done. That particular bit of history will never bother you again. I hope you're happy now.
You throw away a book from the Trials of the Braves.
